\varepsilon<\limsup_{n\to \infty}\frac{1}{n}\sum_{k=0}^{n-1}f\circ T^k(x) = \limsup_{n\to\infty}\frac{1}{n}f(x) + \frac{1}{n}\sum_{k=0}^{n-2}f\circ T^{k}(T(x)).
\limsup_{n\to \infty}\frac{1}{n}\sum_{k=0}^{n-2}f\circ T^k(T(x)) = \limsup_{n\to \infty}\frac{n-1}{n}\frac{1}{n-1}\sum_{k=0}^{n-2}f\circ T^k(T(x)).
